# Memex sidecar state.
# Spaced-repetition scheduling lives here (T11). Personal review history is
# noisy in commit history and rarely useful to teammates — keeping it local-only
# avoids polluting diffs and keeps each user's queue private.
.sr-state.json

# Cached search index (Tantivy). Always regenerable from the markdown corpus.
.search/

# OS / editor noise.
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
.idea/
.vscode/
